These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Movie-Genre: zombie, action, documentary, superhero
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Movie-Genre:documentary##1
2. Movie-Genre:superhero is on the far left##1
3. Movie-Genre:documentary is between Movie-Genre:action and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero | zombie | documentary   | action |

