.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Game: whist, go, domino, snooker
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Game:domino and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Game:snooker is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Game:whist is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | go | whist | domino | snooker |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

