3. Nationality:british is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:french is on the left of Game:snooker##1
5. Game:domino == Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game          | mah-jongg    | canasta | domino   | snooker  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

